room_title: Escape room "Blitzkrieg" by Clue IQ in Frederick
room_address: 103 S. Carroll St, Suite 1A, Frederick, MD 21701
room_description: In the midst of WWII, you will join an Allied commando team tasked with recovering a mysterious artifact from a secret German vault. Your team will test your training against mechanical, tactical, strategic and mental puzzles. The fate of the world depends on defeating the mystical and enigmatic Brotherhood of the Black Sun and recovering the mysterious Artifact in their possession.
